Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.35,0:24:02.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A family accursed by a dog...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.02,0:24:04.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One more victim has fallen prey to the diabolical canine!
